description: This file declares APIs for handling ASN.1 attribute objects in the context of the Advanced Networking Service Container (ANSC). It defines functions for creating ASN.1 attributes and parsing ASN.1 data, with additional licensing and module documentation.

methods.name: AnscAsn1AttrCreate
methods.description: Creates a new ASN.1 attribute object with specified type, number, and implicit flag.

methods.name: AnscAsn1AttrParsingData
methods.description: Parses ASN.1 data from the provided buffer to produce an ASN.1 attribute object.
